data.text: @_moderneve You aren’t whining. You know I’m always a WhatsApp away. Let’s go on vacation.
@_moderneve You're not whining, that is a lot for anyone to handle! It's so good for you to express how completely shitty the last couple of years have been and we're all here for you.

@_moderneve I’m so sorry. You’ve suffered more than a person should ever have to in these past two years. And expressing these truly justified feelings is not whining. Let it out. We’re here for you 💜💜💜
@_moderneve Oh my gosh, Katy, I’m so sorry. That sounds so heartbreaking and difficult. 😔 Sending you a big hug! ❤️
@_moderneve Oh Katy. I wish there was something I could do. I'm so sorry you're going through all this.
@_moderneve Sending you a bit of peace and comfort. 💙 https://t.co/S8NPRmj2Yn
@ellemceebee @_moderneve I cannot begin to imagine this stress, anguish, and loneliness. I wish I could physically help. Sending love and strength. You are truly held in my thoughts.
